'''三氟合锰(II)酸钾'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为KMnF<sub>3</sub>。它是[[立方晶系|立方晶系]]的浅粉色晶体，[[空间群|空间群]]''Pm''{{overline|3}}''m''。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Acta Crystallographica Section B Structural Science|volume=60|issue=4|issn=0108-7681|date=2004-08-01|pages=359–368|doi=10.1107/S0108768104009437|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108768104009437|title=Electron density and electrostatic potential of KMnF 3 : a phase-transition study|accessdate=2021-01-07|author=Yury Ivanov, Tatsuya Nimura, Kiyoaki Tanaka|archive-date=2018-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180604183918/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108768104009437}}</ref>它可由[[溴化锰|溴化锰]]（或[[氯化锰|氯化锰]]<ref name=Hoppe>Hoppe, Rudolf; Liebe, Werner; Dahne, Wolfgang. Fluomanganates of the alkali metals. ''Zeitschrift fuer Anorganische und Allgemeine Chemie'', 1961. 307. 276-289.</ref>）和[[氟化钾|氟化钾]]在[[甲醇|甲醇]]中反应制得。<ref name=David />它和[[氟气|氟气]]反应，可以得到KMnF<sub>5</sub>。<ref name=Hoppe />

